            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國家庭淨資產增加2.2萬億美元 升至紀錄新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 隨著年末股市持續上漲，美國家庭財富第四季度升至紀錄新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會周四公佈的報告顯示，家庭淨資產較前一季度增加2.2萬億美元，達到184.1萬億美元。其中，美國家庭持有的股票資產價值增加1.6萬億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普500指數第四季度延續漲勢並創紀錄，提振投資者財富。市場對人工智能以及企業盈利前景的樂觀情緒推動股價上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報告還顯示，家庭持有的房地產資產價值減少約3470億美元，反映房地產市場表現疲軟。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f3062a27-dce2-31ab-a71b-854c4847ddaf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，消費者借貸以折年率3.3%的速度成長，為2025年第一季度以來最慢。非按揭消費者信貸成長加快，而按揭貸款增速明顯放緩。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">企業債務餘額以折年率2.4%的速度成長，為一年來最慢。在公共部門方面，州和地方政府債務幾無成長，而聯邦政府借款增速強勁。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">包括儲蓄賬戶、支票賬戶和貨幣市場基金在內，家庭和非營利組織持有的存款成長3.3%，升至紀錄新高20.5萬億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Household Net Worth Climbs $2.2 Trillion to Fresh Record (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jarrell Dillard.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E6%B7%A8%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A02-2%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-164524973.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 01:16:04",
